citation.case_name: Ticor Title Insurance Co. v. Brown

html_with_citations:
510 U.S. 810

Ticor Title Insurance Co. et al.
v.
Brown et al.

No. 92-1988.

Supreme Court of United States.

October 4, 1993.

1

Appeal from the C. A. 9th Cir.

2

Certiorari granted limited to Question 1 presented by the petition. Brief of petitioners is to be filed with the Clerk and served upon opposing counsel on or before 3 p.m., Tuesday, November 16, 1993. Brief of respondents is to be filed with the Clerk and served upon opposing counsel on or before 3 p.m., Tuesday, December 14, 1993. A reply brief, if any, is to be filed with the Clerk and served upon opposing counsel on or before 3 p.m., Wednesday, January 5, 1994. This Court's Rule 29 does not apply. Reported below: 982 F. 2d 386.
